lead_paragraph: Yarelys Barrios of Cuba was stripped of the silver medal in the women's discus from the 2008 Beijing Olympics on Thursday after testing positive in a reanalysis of her doping samples.

headline.print_headline: Cuban Stripped of Silver Medal in 2008 Discus for Doping
